These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, polish
2 different games are played: snooker, billiard
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, dahlia
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, sports
1. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
2. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
3. the turkish is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Nationality      | polish     | turkish      |
| Game          | billiard | snooker    |
| Flower         | dahlia   | amaryllis |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | sports      |

