.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
2 different pets are kept: frog, snake
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, french
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, montecristo
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the canadian##5
3. the french is not to the right of the canadian##8
4. the chaman-smoker is not the owner of the snake##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Pet       | frog         | snake |
| Nationality         | french | canadian   |
| Cigar   | chaman               | montecristo  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: grapes, potato
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, photography
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, japanese
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk
1. the australian is in an odd position##4
2. the japanese is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Food   | grapes       | potato |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks       | photography    |
| Nationality   | australian | japanese |
| Beverage           | almond-milk        | soy-milk   |

