House: modern, futuristic
There are 2 different nationalities: german, polish
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, coral
1. the german is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
2. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person who likes coral##8
3. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Game         | snooker | poker  |
| House           | futuristic  | modern |
| Nationality   | polish | german   |
| Color     | coral   | yellow |

