There are 2 different nationalities: german, indian
1. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
2. the german is the german##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
4. the german is not to the right of the indian##8
5. the indian is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| Birthday        | november | december            |
| Hobby       | writing | chess              |
| Pet         | rabbit  | snake |
| Nationality   | german     | indian         |

